  "remarks": "Cooperated in KOMID’s international sales of weapons. KOMID is a sanctioned entity under Australian sanctions law.; Listing: Listed on: 17 Aug. 2017. Continued in effect for a further three years by Declaration of the Minister for Foreign Affairs made on 23 May 2020 pursuant to regulation 9(3) of the Autonomous Sanctions Regulations 2011.  Re-listed on 22 May 2023 under the Autonomous Sanctions (Designated Persons and Entities and Declared Persons - Democratic People's Republic of Korea) Amendment (No. 1) Instrument 2023.",
